    public class Kunde

    Represents a customer. A customer can be edited and deleted Hinweis: Die Klasse mussten wir leider public lassen, da wir sonst keine neu Instanz eines Kunden in der Factory Klasse anlegen können

    • Constructor Detail

      • Kunde

        public Kunde(java.lang.String type,
             java.lang.String name,
             java.lang.String vorname,
             java.lang.String straße,
             int hausnummer,
             int postleitzahl,
             java.lang.String stadt,
             java.lang.String land,
             java.lang.String telefon,
             int kundennummer,
             java.lang.String notiz)
        Creates a new customer with all the parameters.
        Parameters:
        type - The type of our person. In this case: customer
        name - surname of this customer
        vorname - first name of the customer
        straße - street in which the customer lives
        hausnummer - house number
        postleitzahl - zip code of the city, where the customer lives
        stadt - city, in which the customer lives
        land - country, in which the customer lives
        telefon - telephone number from the customer
        kundennummer - the customer number
        notiz - notes regarding the customer
